of very few there that held no worship for the Olympian Gods, but indeed she gave great love to the Mother Goddess Gaia . . . for Alysia-Samsara herself was Gaia's direct blood daughter. Though very few knew of it all.<br>
<br>
She looked around for this Priestess Alex she was told about. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">~*~ Jessica ~*~<br>
