<br>
Alexiares loved to dance.  She had since she was a small child.  And knew that teaching that gift was a blessing that gave her great happiness.  Moving slowely, her light almost sheer clothes flowed about her body.  While gold braclets and belts jingled softly with her movement.  Around her ankles were more small golden bells.  And even some of her pupils wore a little golden bell tied by woven cord around their ankles.  Each color cord meaning the child's dancing level. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=daughterofshylock>Daughter of Shylock</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.picturesof.net/_wallpaper/rose_Dsc08151_WP.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Golden Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 393<br> <font color=#993300>(5/12/03 6:40 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> ....</span><hr size=1> Alysia watched the dancers and smiled lightly looking to the children.<br>
She placed a small hand on her slightly oversized stomach and smiled softly.<br>
<br>
She continued to remain there in silence, until she was noticed. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=alexiares>Alexiares</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 31<br> <font color=#993300>(5/16/03 8:57 pm)</font><br>     <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/queenhippolyte/images/alexiares.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ....</span><hr size=1> Spinning around with her students, Alexiares saw the northern queen standing watching.  She almost stumbled when she realized that she being watched by Vasilissa Alysia.  Alexiares stopped dancing and then clapped her hands to the children.  With a gentle smile, she released them.  The children ran off laughing and some even dancing off.<br>
<br>
Alexiares watched them for a moment and then looked at the northern queen.  She walked over with a large smile, &quot;It is a great honor to receive you into this temple, Vasilissa Alysia.  What brings you this far from home?&quot;   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=daughterofshylock>Daughter of Shylock</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.picturesof.net/_wallpaper/rose_Dsc08151_WP.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Golden Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 424<br> <font color=#993300>(5/19/03 5:43 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> ...</span><hr size=1> Alysia smirked a bit towards the young girl.<br>
<br>
&quot;My son spoke of you.&quot; She smiled. &quot;He spoke of an amazon who wished not to stay in the quarters with two Amazon Princes.&quot; She looked to Alexiares.<br>
<br>
&quot;He, as well as I find that honorable of an amazon.&quot;<br>
<br>
She began to walk among the temple looking around.<br>
<br>
&quot;I understand that this temple is dedicated to the Goddesses yes? I wonder, is Gaia considered worthy of worship here?&quot;<br>
<br>
She continued to walk around.<br>
<br>
&quot;I am greatly eager to bring my athelfi here if there is a dedication unto Gaia as well. We Northern Sisters need a place to worship among our athelfi as well.&quot; she smiled softly to her. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=alexiares>Alexiares</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 37<br> <font color=#993300>(5/22/03 11:00 am)</font><br>     <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/queenhippolyte/images/alexiares.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ...</span><hr size=1> Alexiares laughed softly and then whispered to Alysia.  &quot;Vasilissa, all Olympians and Greek Gods are worshipped here.  And even those who our allied Trojans do not.  We are hoping that we can teach them the blessings of them as well.  So, yes, Gaia is certainly worshipped here.  Certainly, since she is the mother of so many.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;I would be proud if your athelfi brought more prayers to the great Goddess Gaia to this temple,&quot; Alexiares said, glancing around at the activity around them.  A small child ran by and grinned then giggled as he ran off passed the two of them.  &quot;As you can see, we teach to the very young.  So, the worship of the Gods will not be forgotten.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=alexiares>Alexiares</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 50<br> <font color=#993300>(6/1/03 6:39 pm)</font><br>     <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A Northern Worshiper</span><hr size=1> Move topic to <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://pub163.ezboard.com/fmythicalodysseyforumfrm41">pub163.ezboard.com/fmythi...forumfrm41</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--> <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm78.showNextMessage?topicID=2.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm78.emailToFriend?topicID=2.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm78.threadControl?topicID=2.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/deleteThreadFire.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm78.subscribeUnregiste